snippet.title: The Sims 4™ Realm of Magic: Official Gameplay
snippet.description:
Learn the craft of wizardry, summon a familiar for protection, and immerse yourself in The Sims 4: Realm of Magic!*

Available September 10, 2019 on PC and Mac and October 15, 2019 for console. 

Learn more about this Game Pack: http://x.ea.com/59667.

*REQUIRES THE SIMS 4 GAME (SOLD SEPARATELY) AND ALL GAME UPDATES TO PLAY. SEE MINIMUM SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS FOR THIS PACK.
